Package cn.nukkit.form.window

Class Form<T extends Response>

java.lang.Object
cn.nukkit.form.window.Form<T>
Type Parameters:
T - A response object
Direct Known Subclasses:
CustomForm, ModalForm, SimpleForm
public abstract class Form<T extends Response> extends Object
Abstract class used to dynamically generate and send forms to players.
